{"first_name":"Esteban","last_name":"Contreras","permalink":"esteban-contreras-2","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/person/esteban-contreras-2","homepage_url":"http://www.estebancontreras.com","birthplace":"Guatemala City, Guatemala","twitter_username":"socialnerdia","blog_url":"http://www.socialnerdia.com","blog_feed_url":"http://www.socialnerdia.com/blog/rss.xml","affiliation_name":"Sprinklr","born_year":null,"born_month":null,"born_day":null,"tag_list":"sprinklr, social-nerdia, samsung, social-media, marketing, strategist, consultant","alias_list":null,"created_at":"Wed Sep 26 20:49:22 UTC 2012","updated_at":"Fri Oct 12 20:32:21 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Esteban Contreras is founder of Social Nerdia, a consultancy and blog focused on the convergence of technology, marketing and social media. www.socialnerdia.com</p>\n\n<p>Esteban serves as Account Director and Strategist for NYC-based Sprinklr, a leader enterprise SMMS platform.</p>\n\n<p>Esteban has world-class level of social strategy experience, and a deep knowledge of the social technology landscape. Rated one of PR News&#8217; 15-to-Watch in 2011, Esteban is the former Social Media Marketing Manager for Samsung USA, where he led strategy, execution and management of the brand&#8217;s US social media presence, activations like SXSW interactive, and integration of social tech &amp; game mechanics on campaigns and Samsung.com. He&#8217;s been a featured speaker at conferences like SXSWi, CES, CSM Summit, BlogWorld, The Gamification Summit, Internet Week, DCM East &amp; M2C.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to Samsung, Esteban was a Technology Consultant for the consulting division of Amdocs, Inc. He also advises SMBs like Cucupons.com, Torreblanca, and Unified Social Media.</p>\n\n<p>Born in Guatemala City, Esteban has lived in Dallas TX, Jersey City NJ and now Vancouver BC. You can learn more at www.estebancontreras.com.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,143],"assets/images/resized/0021/3201/213201v2-max-150x150.